/li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword </a></i> <small>(2003)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i> <small>(2010)</small></li></ul></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Blood_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"Blood of the Dragon\">Blood of the Dragon</a></i> <small>(1996)</small></li>\n<li><i><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Path of the Dragon</a></i> <small>(2000)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Arms_of_the_Kraken\" title=\"Arms of the Kraken\">Arms of the Kraken</a></i> <small>(2002)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i> <small>(2013)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rogue_Prince\" title=\"The Rogue Prince\">The Rogue Prince</a></i> <small>(2014)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> <small>(2017)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Histories</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> <small>(2014)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> <small>(2018)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> <small>(2022)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Blood_%26_Fire\" title=\"Blood &amp; Fire\">Blood &amp; Fire</a></i> <small>(TBA)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Maps</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i> <small>(2012)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible collapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:ASOIAF\" title=\"Template talk:ASOIAF\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:ASOIAF&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Derived_works\" title=\"Derived works\">Derived works</a> from the world of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Games</td><td styl